{"tid":979161,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《死神來了》拍第六集","createTime":"2019-01-12T13:28:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-15T03:24:27.000Z","uid":41343,"like":22,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"fe033efce3087e4f8c065bf7607123b31bee72f6","tid":979161,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:28:37.000Z","msg":"恐怖片系列《死神來了》（Final Destination）曾大受歡迎，當中各種可怕死狀實在令觀眾大開眼界。<br />\n<br />\n自從首集於2000年開畫後，先後拍成五部同系列電影，當中以09年嘅《死神4來了》（The Final Destination）票房最為理想，而五片在全球總票房累積達6.65億美元（約51.87億港元），可惜後期卻被指越拍越爛，曾揚言11年嘅《死神5來了》（The Final Destination 5）會係最後一部。<br />\n<br />\n事隔八年，電影公司New Line Cinema宣佈《死神來了》會開拍第6集，由《恐懼鬥室》（Saw）系列嘅Marcus Dunstan同埋Patrick Melton負責撰寫劇本，但劇情暫時仍大賣關子。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190112/59135380\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59135380&d=VoBFsfm%2BAkNe8%2BlrT9I1H7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=96fd5ee8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190112%2F59135380&h=55f866a5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190112/59135380</a>"},{"pid":"b87a34fc245dc95eb836891d7d4212b32eb5de79","tid":979161,"uid":8042,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"第5集整咗個loop咪幾好<br />\n何必再做爛"},{"pid":"a5f7d54899c0078eb44100c10831ccd61b7e2f8b","tid":979161,"uid":41343,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b87a34fc245dc95eb836891d7d4212b32eb5de79","tid":979161,"uid":8042,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"第5集整咗個loop咪幾好<br />\n何必再做爛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:34:19.000Z","msg":"torture porn 都過左氣"},{"pid":"f0be918dbc338266b5bf5e773ba0f5b2b8fea6aa","tid":979161,"uid":224058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019